 188:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_i2c.c **** /**
 189:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_i2c.c ****   * @brief  config own address1.
 190:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_i2c.c ****   * @param  i2c_x: to select the i2c peripheral.
 191:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_i2c.c ****   *         this parameter can be one of the following values:
 192:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_i2c.c ****   *         I2C1, I2C2, I2C3.
 193:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_i2c.c ****   * @param  mode
 194:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_i2c.c ****   *         this parameter can be one of the following values:
 195:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_i2c.c ****   *         - I2C_ADDRESS_MODE_7BIT: 7bit address.
 196:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_i2c.c ****   *         - I2C_ADDRESS_MODE_10BIT: 10bit address.
 197:libraries/drivers/src/at32f403a_407_i2c.c ****   * @param  address: own address1, such as 0xb0.
